{"type":"article_comment","id":155199,"parentType":"article","parentId":10623,"uid":766,"contents":"蔥友啊，<br>\n品牌設計不是那麼容易的，<br>\n至少最基本的標準字體、標準色都要有的。<br>\n如果蔥友對品牌設計有興趣，<br>\n可以翻翻企業形象系統手冊（CIS手冊）來看，<br>\n雖然品蔥網站設計不需要到這麼嚴謹，但基本概念還是建議要有，<br>\n我來發幾張台灣故宮博物院的CIS手冊給對相關設計有興趣的蔥友們看看。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/stghQXh.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/stghQXh.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/stghQXh.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/HdFLTSj.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HdFLTSj.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/HdFLTSj.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mZOlq5H.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mZOlq5H.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mZOlq5H.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rd5rB1e.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rd5rB1e.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rd5rB1e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RzvABsL.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RzvABsL.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RzvABsL.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/it4dn0m.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/it4dn0m.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/it4dn0m.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/q6l37Aw.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q6l37Aw.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/q6l37Aw.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n更詳盡的內容我就不貼了，蔥友可以去故宮官網看。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.npm.gov.tw/Article.aspx?sNo=02009979\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">資料來源：故宮博物院官網，下拉有PDF檔下載連結</a>","date":"201